node.text: Thank you to @ardenfilmco for capturing such a special day in our lives 💕 We’re so incredibly happy we went with them to film our big day! There were so many small, special moments throughout the day that we both had forgotten about and @ardenfilmco was able to capture them for us. And of course, happy Valentine’s Day to my hubby @cmdorsch on our first Valentine’s Day as a married couple! I love you so much!!! node.text: My cuties 👶🏼🐶 Kennedy is such a happy baby! She honestly smiles like this all day long 🥺 but to be honest, even though *she* is so happy, *I* sometimes feel guilty for not feeling as happy as I think I should feel. I’ve really been struggling with anxiety as a new mom… I worry about everything pertaining to Kennedy, all the time, big and small things, realistic things and unrealistic things. I have trouble living in the moment and truly enjoying my baby because of it. From some of the DMs you’ve sent, it sounds like a lot of you feel or have felt the same. If you’ve been through this before, I’d love to know what helped you. 💗 #newmom #momandbaby #momlife
